    "By contrast, value-based methods, such as deep Q-learning [664] (Appendix C.2) learn the value function from which the optimal policy is selected.",
    "Actor-critic methods, such as proximal policy optimization [665] combine the ideas with an actor that performs a policy and a critic that judges its quality.",
    "Both can be modeled by NNs.",
    "C.1 Deep policy networksIn deep policy networks, the policy, i.e., the mapping of states to actions, is modeled by a NN â = π(s; θ).",
